ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Excellent overview for someone like myself who doesn't have much background.

i would recommend this course to anyone in humanities - especially undergraduates. In one single course, a student learns the complexity facing future world politics. I cannot imagine a better way to cover some much material in such an efficient way.
take it if you have limited historical and political background on china
If it is first time to learn about China, take it. If not, think it carefully. Still good class, though.
